{"type": "article", "id": 31274, "title": "中国将成为第一大零售市场，以及，Stamped 与 PUMA 再度合作 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-08-22T02:26:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 743, "name": "零售"}, {"id": 2636, "name": "Swatch"}, {"id": 27421, "name": "Beams"}, {"id": 31760, "name": "NIKE Lab"}, {"id": 325, "name": "Fendi"}, {"id": 26358, "name": "A Bathing Ape"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160822095440cn3MsKCUTS6VYNGA.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/daniella-helayel-british-high-street-brand-monsoon-duchess-of-cambridge-kate-middleton-10511020/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Issa London 的创始人及创意总监 Daniella Issa Helayel 要与 Monsoon 合作 </b></a>| 作为 Kate 王妃喜爱的品牌，Issa London 宣布与英国的时尚电商 Monsoon 合作，推出一系列裙装胶囊系列。&nbsp;</p><p><b style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/retail-features/china-retail-market-set-to-eclipse-u-s-10510737/\" rel=\"nofollow\">中国将超越美国成为全球第一大零售市场</a></b> | 2016 年，中国的零售市场规模将达到 4.89 兆美元，超过美国市场的 4.82 兆美元，成为世界第一大零售市场。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/foot-locker-earnings-apparel-10510860/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>世界最大的体育用品网络零售商 Foot Locker 第二季度股票大涨</b></a> | 由于限定款的运动系列产品在第二季度大卖，Foot Locker 的股票大涨了 9%，至 67.67 美元每股。净收入涨至 1.27 亿美元，去年同期则为 1.19 亿美元。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>Fendi 2016 初秋首饰系列大玩摇滚元素，配色非常丰富。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091358al6Gnw1OZXhJKmPy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091352fSjF3OzhAWKMCJGu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091345mnBtYJ7bcI1qfyx4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091336SB9zrG7o8jKlIWgd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">BEAMS PLUS 发布了 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/beams-plus-2016-fall-winter-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">2016 秋冬系列</a>预览，主打层次丰富的户外风格，融合了军装、格纹、针织等多种元素。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091446GDT7ze4ymClFdKR8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091436r9Ic0uAJ7vVNX3ez.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091429ETzS4dv5MHCkKpfl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091423EbWLODRpsrUVJNoA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091416zROnwlMV9bAvrLKh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">SWATCH 2016 秋冬新品系列手表上线，此次的新品有 「建筑多元」「Grüezi All！」「自由之声」「也是很久很久以前」「魔幻冬季」等多个系列。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091524hCUiwgLq9Z7AVu3E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666449\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091519jLNxBTAfY1csFWqQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667316\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091512HujJUn8iL9mEkclP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608220915058wvz79SZsFJuXdOW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/a-bathing-ape-2016-indigo-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">A Bathing Ape 发布 2016 秋冬日本蓝染“ indigo ” </a>系列，该系列产品采用了日本特有的靛蓝染色技术，涵盖了卫衣、帽衫、T-Shirt 和运动裤等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091601rFZzcnbX3xmqaHd1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091555WqbwBPF9x0sIjafv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608220915499LKtplegUAGNTkrJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091543RpF9DIqNon56iuhj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608220915342WtNzp0gePfjIuDL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Air Max 96 诞生 20 周年之际，NIKE Lab 推出了<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/nikelab-air-max-1-deluxe\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Air Max 1 的新系列</a>。其中，这款 Deluxe 系列，采用上乘皮革制作，搭配黑白灰三款颜色，鞋底则有 Nike 字样，呈现出高质感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091631dMiweAoCVJBuNZmv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091626QzoqgZ0inF673pOe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091620Pbxc2Q0VSMw6Iv9k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822091613VMy4qnJwjE0lhf9W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">创立于 2011 年的美式西海岸风格生活方式品牌 Stamped 与 PUMA 再度合作，推出了 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/stampd-puma-2016-fall-winter-apparel\" rel=\"nofollow\">2016 秋冬男女运动休闲服装系列</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822095302oyGZB8YTicOExaKg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822095257dJlR297BxSntIUFk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822095252RdDF73xSJZXgCmuA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160822095244O0IXD4Fzve3b2MUB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}